By: Eckhart
---
The soul, having conquered the multiple heavens and possessed herself of their
mysterious power, is plunged into the unity of the motionless heaven, called
fire or the empyrean, not because it is burning but because it is enlightening,
all who are in this heaven being ablaze with the cherubic light of divine love.
